data.description: Gorgeous Craftsman Home located in the highly desirable gated community of Nature Trail! Backs up to greenspace. Nice Lot! LAP POOL features a waterfall and it is screened in! The pool is heated and it is Saltwater! This home has 4 bedrooms with 3 full bathrooms. Side entry garage. Sprinkler system. WHOLE HOUSE GENERATOR.  Quick close hurricane protection shutters. The kitchen is fully equipped with a gas stove/oven combo, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a fabulous butlers pantry. The pantry is ideal for storing larger kitchen items and serving dishes. Primary bedroom is tucked away for privacy from the other bedrooms. The room features a SPLIT AC WALL UNIT for those that like to sleep with colder air. There is a door that leads out from the bedroom to the screened in porch and makes a great spot for relaxing. The primary bathroom includes a garden tub, shower, double vanity and a huge walk in closet with built ins. There is a storage shed that is located on the side of the home. Plenty of space to store pool floats and garden tools. Security system. Surround sound.  Nature Trail features walking trails, community clubhouse, exercise room, community pool, tennis and basketball courts, and a playground. This home is ready for you today. Call for your personal showing.
